data.description: Exquisite home with beautiful finish out. Soaring ceilings, study, formal dining, butlers pantry, gourmet kitchen with gas cook top, double built in ovens, built in microwave, stainless appliances, granite, island and all open to the living room. The stone floor to ceiling fireplace is a beautiful accent in the corner. Owners retreat is TEXAS sized with luxury bath attached. All secondary bedrooms are upstairs along with a game and media room!
